edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.gnsapp.clientCommandProcessor.commandSupport

Class GroupAccess

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umass.cs.gnsserver.gnsapp.clientCommandProcessor.commandSupport.GroupAccess

  • public class GroupAccess
extends Object
    GroupAccess provides an interface to the group information in the GNS. The members of a group are stored in a record in each guid whose key is the GROUP string. There is also a "reverse" link (GROUPS) stored in each guid which is the groups that the guid is a member of. The reverse link means that we can check for membership of a guid without going to a different NS.
    Author:
    westy
